## Architecture

| Layer | Path | Owner | Mutability |
|---|---|---|---|
| Raw sources | `{{RAW_DIR}}/` | human curates | **immutable** |
| The wiki (extraction) | `{{WIKI_DIR}}/` | LLM | extraction only |
| Output (synthesis) | `{{OUTPUT_DIR}}/` | LLM | editorial/applied |
| Memory | `.memory/` | LLM | cross-session, in-repo |
| Schema | `CLAUDE.md` + `AGENTS.md` | co-evolved | mirrored |

