в”њв”Ђв”Ђ log.md              в†ђ append-only chronological record
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ _templates/         в†ђ page templates
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sources/            в†ђ one page per document
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ {{ENTITY_DIR}}/     в†ђ one page per person/org/entity (e.g. authors/)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ concepts/           в†ђ one page per idea/theme
в””в”Ђв”Ђ frameworks/         в†ђ one page per named model/system
